{"serial": "63003", "department_serial": 59, "code": "SS1010", "class": "*", "name": {"en": "Introduction to Earth system Science", "ch": "地球系統科學概論"}, "notice": {"en": "", "ch": "與GP1010及AP1010合班上課"}, "instructor": {"en": ["Yen, Horng-Yuan", "Chien, Hwa", "Chung, Kao-Shen", "Chen, Pei-Yuan", "Liu, Jann-Yeng"], "ch": ["顏宏元", "錢樺", "鍾高陞", "陳沛芫", "劉正彥"]}, "credits": 2, "time_loc": [{"time": {"week": 4, "session": ["A", "B"]}, "loc": {"building": "TR", "room": "A203"}}], "isRequired": false, "isFullSem": false, "MaxStu": -1, "department": {"ch": "太空科學與工程學系", "en": "Department of Space Science and Engineering"}, "system": {"ch": "學士班", "en": "Undergraduate Programme"}, "language": {"ch": "國語", "en": "Chinese"}, "card": {"ch": "不使用", "en": "None"}, "assigned": 0, "selected": 34, "remark": {"ch": "與GP1010及AP1010合班上課", "en": ""}, "goal": {"ch": "“讓學生由認識地球與太空環境，了解我們日常生活與地球系統和日地太空環境之間密切的關係。藉由瞭解，學生可學會保護自己，避免因無知，造成生命財產的損失。也藉由瞭解，學生們將學會如何為環境保護盡一份心力。\n地球物理和地震部分：增進對地球的認識，並提供最好的保護方法。“", "en": "The objective of this course is to let students understand how the physical processes in the Earth system and the solar-terrestrial system affect our daily life. Let students learn to protect themselves from the nature disaster and learn to conserve our nature environment."}, "outline": {"ch": "“太空部分：\n1. 認識日地太空環境\n2. 認識太空觀測與太空活動\n3. 認識太空天氣\n4. 太空天氣如何影響日常生活\n大氣部分：\n1. 從觀測認識地球大氣\n2. 大氣運動以及其影響的層面\n3. 氣候變遷與全球暖化\n4. 大氣圈與其他圈之交互作用\n地球物理和地震部分：\n1. 地震、火山、板塊\n2. 天然災害：地震、海嘯、火山、山崩土石流、水災\n3. 地震前兆研究、地震預警\n4. 台灣造山運動極地體構造研究“", "en": "“Space Physics:\n1. Introduction to the Solar-Terrestrial Space Environment\n2. Introduction to Space Observation and Space Life\n3. Introduction to Space Weather\n4. Space Weather and You“\n“Atmospheric Science“\n1. Understand the Earth’s atmosphere from observations\n2. Atmospheric movement and its impact\n3. Climate change and global warming\n4. Interaction between the atmosphere and other spheres"}, "textbook": {"ch": "“太空部分: 上課講義\n地球物理和地震部分：上課講義、參考自編講義“\n“大氣科學“: 上課講義、相關時事資訊